### Our Strategic Approach

**Differentiation:** This post will be the only one on the SERP that treats bridesmaid nail coordination as a design problem with a practical solution framework — not a gallery of pretty options. We frame the central question as: how do you create visual harmony in a group photo when five people have different skin tones, personal preferences, and potentially different dress colours? Every design section answers that question.

